summary: An ordinance accepting a deed to the City of Seattle executed on Julius Schweigart and Cora L. Schweigart, his wife, dated June 1, 1910, to a portion of lots 29, 30, 31, 32, 33, block 7, Supplemental Plat of blocks 7 and 10, McKenzie & Dempsey's Lake Washington Addition, for public street and sidewalk purposes only.
